STATE EX REL. MANGUN
v.
OLIVITO 2018-1204 Supreme Court of Ohio. October 19, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS ORDERS

In Mandamus. Cause returned to the regular docket under S.Ct.Prac.R. 19.01. Respondent ordered to file a response to the complaint within 21 days. Relator's amended motion to lift stay denied as moot.
